episodes.title: She Is Trapped in a TikTok cult
episodes.description:
This TikTok dancer with millions of fans looks COMPLETELY DIFFERENT now... a chilling reminder that even our dreams can turn into nightmares.

This cult is stealing talented creators and we need to help!

Share this video to expose them and bring Miranda and everyone still trapped in that place back to their real selves.

Remember, fame is fleeting, but family and your most authentic self is priceless...
